
  At least 12 years relevant working experience in local building construction. 
  Accredited as C&amp;S Resident Engineer with the Joint Accreditation Committee of the Institution of Engineers Singapore (IES) and the Association of Consulting Engineers Singapore (ACES). 
  To possess and demonstrate track record(s) of being an Overall coordinator/team leader for team of Site Supervisors for projects with value of building works &gt; $75 million. 
  Proficient in using Microsoft Word, Excel and Powerpoint. 
  Demonstrate effective interpersonal skills, able to communicate effectively with various project stakeholders. 
  Familiarity with Building Control Regulations 2003, Part III on “Duties of Qualified Persons, Site Supervisors and Builders During Construction” 
  Familiarity with the Public Service Sector Conditions of Contract (PSSCOC) for Construction Works
